{"tid":2222081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然間入院 而家係醫院度醒左回緊氣","createTime":"2020-09-29T00:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T14:14:57.000Z","uid":30000,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5dacbb11ebeb1f6cfe08898ee456e04af4384799","tid":2222081,"uid":30000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"呢排天氣轉 突然間琴晚訓訓下訓唔到 即咳醒左<br />\n老母驚我有事 即刻送左入院 <br />\n問左醫生而家話未敢俾我出去住 <br />\n始終係漏夜上房<br />\n<br />\n突然之間覺得原來人生真係好唏噓 <br />\n成日覺得自己都好多野未做 <br />\n但最後可能上路個時又係得自己一個<br />\n<br />\n同埋 健康真係好重要 <br />\n希望今年天氣可以好過啲 <br />\n咁就唔洗咁痛苦"},{"pid":"74840a4ddfbca5986c0227af8bc16d944b197fca","tid":2222081,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725887a47015dea73634d19a3f5d56cb7a2fe4dd","tid":2222081,"uid":99328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T00:56:00.000Z","msg":"加油 祝早日康復"},{"pid":"1b2c9913d4e514b82f475efe32e1cf2e06ebedd7","tid":2222081,"uid":52132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T00:56:13.000Z","msg":"Add oil"},{"pid":"b6e18102f4a1942738ed7059280b2ec93108eaf6","tid":2222081,"uid":306360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:00:51.000Z","msg":"所以一定要小心飲食同運動習俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449b4240aa1034a497491dd91c3b2bcf82aebf9c","tid":2222081,"uid":238798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T01:08:39.000Z","msg":"盡力珍惜所愛之人 無愧於心<br />\n人生無常 及時行樂<